<item>
            <title>[LU-19887] sanity test_300ug: 12MDT failed to migrate overstriped directory</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19887</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@dilger.ca&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/f30af87a-6852-447c-8828-0feee19834e7&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/f30af87a-6852-447c-8828-0feee19834e7&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_300ug failed with the following error when run with a large number of MDTs.  In the above test it failed with &quot;&lt;tt&gt;Test-Parameters: mdscount=3 mdtcount=12&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; for patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/56384&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/56384&lt;/a&gt; (&quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14058&quot; title=&quot;Create tests for large number of MDTs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-14058&quot;&gt;LU-14058&lt;/a&gt; tests: clean up sanity.sh MDT name generation&quot;).  It is failing while migrating an overstriped directory with 12 x 5 = 60 stripes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;LustreError: cowardly refusing to write 9874 bytes in a page
LustreError: 689710:0:(lod_object.c:905:lod_load_lmv_shards()) lustre-MDT0003-mdtlov: invalid shard name 
LustreError: 689710:0:(mdt_reint.c:2531:mdt_reint_migrate()) lustre-MDT0003: migrate [0x200007163:0xbc:0x0]/f300ug.sanity failed: rc = -22
(4) failed to migrate overstriped directory
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/107715&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/107715&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-362.24.1.el9_3.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/107715&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/107715&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-362.24.1_lustre.el9.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;







